contentrichtext.text: '''ZiS''' (Russian: ''Zavod imeni Stalina'', 'Factory named for Stalin') may refer to: * [[Zavod imeni Likhacheva]] of Moscow, formerly Automotive Factory No. 2 Zavod imeni Stalina, and its products: ** [[ZiS-101]] limousine ** [[ZiS-110]] limousine ** [[ZiS-150]] ** [[ZiS-152]] ([[BTR-152]]) armoured personnel carrier ** [[GM_"old-look"_transit_bus#ZIS-154|ZiS-154]] - transit bus ** [[GM_"old-look"_transit_bus#ZIS-155|ZiS-155]] - transit bus * [[Artillery Factory No. 92]], Zavod imeni Stalina of Gorky, and its products: ** [[ZiS-2]] 57mm antitank gun ** [[ZiS-3]] 76.2mm divisional gun ** [[ZiS-5]] 76.2mm tank gun (version of the [[F-34 tank gun]]) ** [[ZiS-30]] self-propelled antitank gun ** [[ZiS-S-53]] 85mm tank gun [[Category:Companies of the Soviet Union]] [[Category:Bus manufacturers]] [[Category:Military vehicle manufacturers]] {{disambig}}
